<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF5F6AE0FCE59CAE1D61B0EB" pageId="164" pageNumber="926" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF5F6AE0FCE59CAE1D61B0EB" blockId="164.[792,1384,2689,3112]" pageId="164" pageNumber="926">
Subgenus Pyzonix; 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5F6AE0FBDD9CAE1A95B026" baseAuthorityName="Le Conte" baseAuthorityYear="1831" box="[1057,1173,2807,2836]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="926" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lucifugus">lucifugus</taxonomicName>
species group. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5F6AE0FCE69D461A2AB00E" baseAuthorityName="Merriam" baseAuthorityYear="1890" box="[794,1066,2847,2876]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="926" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="melanorhinus">Myotis melanorhinus</taxonomicName>
was previously a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5F6AE0FC569D1B1A14B051" baseAuthorityName="Audubon &amp; Bachman" baseAuthorityYear="1842" box="[938,1044,2882,2915]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="927" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="leibii">M. leibii</taxonomicName>
and later 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF5F6AE0FB5F9D1B1B62B051" authorityName="Merriam" authorityYear="1886" box="[1187,1378,2882,2915]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="164" pageNumber="927" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="ciliolabrum">M. ciliolabrum</taxonomicName>
. Morphology and morphometric characters support its full species status. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF5F6AE0FCE49DB11C8DB77D" pageId="164" pageNumber="926" type="distribution">
